Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.35,0:02:02.23,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}living your life don't give up now keep moving on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.42,0:02:07.63,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}君を抱き締める 何度も何度も何度も
