Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不会奏效
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无限拳居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被反弹回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从Mithra Gnis身上确认到高等级灵能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那难道是…Element反应!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说Abductor的操纵者是Element吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.91,0:05:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:41.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逆转的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逆转?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当爱转化为恨之时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切火焰都将被冰封
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光芒将化为黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之就是物理法则的反转
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.69,0:06:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.23,0:06:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jin君…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.61,0:06:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要和我一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往Altair界…没错 前往我所居住的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.14,0:06:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jin君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接纳了我们的大家都在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在一开始就把一切都计划好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.91,0:06:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只为夺走最强的RareIgler
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我这种人不可能为大家所需要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 放开我 Jin君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生异常情况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.99,0:07:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机库内的Vector预备机正企图擅自起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.26,0:07:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,操纵者是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿克巴尔金·巴德巴艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然这家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人的间谍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难怪我总觉得他郁郁寡欢的像有不可告人的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.78,0:07:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准许
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡 助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 太嫩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 这架Abductor
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.20,0:07:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不光是拥有着奇怪的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙和之前战斗时相比也不可同日而语
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.72,0:07:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从次元门那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎有着高密度的能量以拟态管道的形式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:07:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断注入Mithra Gunis体内
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们必须要关闭次元门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能切断输送管道的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,运命的红线
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.69,0:08:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,运命的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红线?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纺织出那残酷命运之人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我速速现身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是你 竟然已经察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花瓣?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.59,0:08:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬间移动?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.99,0:08:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jin君比刚来这里的时候开朗了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些全都是在计划当中的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住嘴!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 Jin君肯定是需要大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.33,0:09:08.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以大家也会需要Jin君的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不会有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.06,0:09:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来晚了么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.27,0:09:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后之子也似乎顺利完成了自己的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 是美型
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.96,0:09:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多纳尔 振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多纳尔!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:09:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好久不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.44,0:10:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是时隔一万两千年 或者是两万四千年呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.15,0:10:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不动?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于大驾光临了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 你那模样多么不堪入目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.43,0:10:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把你的真面目弃置到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉眼所见的容貌仅仅是一种束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.96,0:10:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亦即为对过去的执着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是你这家伙 至今尚未能舍弃过去的容貌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.97,0:10:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罢了 我就单刀直入地说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.10,0:10:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你告诉我阿波罗尼亚丝那闪耀着琥珀色光芒的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 也就是真正的太阳之翼的所在之处
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:10:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你 放我下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.53,0:11:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jin君 求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.21,0:11:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚叶…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.73,0:11:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 就是这个味道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逆转
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.04,0:11:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔君…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的…我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希尔菲!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希尔菲?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最讨厌你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.27,0:12:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自第一眼看到你就觉得你讨厌极了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的希尔菲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.84,0:12:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.26,0:12:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希尔菲?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24}不要 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我要憎恨你 然后杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 让你在我的怀里 永远
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.72,0:12:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.16,0:12:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.65,0:12:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是那时候的男人么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么味道都没有的奇怪男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有味道就等同于不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说把你杀掉也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我让你心脏的血液逆流的话会怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这不是走投无路了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的希望已经全被葬送到黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 回答我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两万四千年的恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳之翼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其在何方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 原来是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:13:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉 一直把你遗忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多纳尔·丹迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有机会再一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.63,0:14:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那貌似是由思念构成的精神体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.53,0:14:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须绪美女士 在司令室里启动Element干扰器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.70,0:14:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.44,0:14:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.41,0:14:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.17,0:14:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安迪 Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了你们也没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我正要挖洞藏身的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙就从头上掉了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这群家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要逆转你们的命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:14:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,办得到的话就试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.51,0:15:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.31,0:15:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪炎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion 立刻再次合体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.27,0:15:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 不想办法应付次元门的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻断的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.26,0:15:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用我的力量的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.34,0:15:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿克巴尔金·巴德巴艾尔  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.29,0:15:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是Jin·无双
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.82,0:15:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是间谍 事到如今还装模作样干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请相信他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 Jin君是我们的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.93,0:15:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚叶 不要被那种家伙骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得我不可相信的话 不相信也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 如果没有我来到这个世界后所获得的阻断的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.73,0:16:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是无法关闭Altair的次元门的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.34,0:16:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:04.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以让我也参与合体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱会跨越星际吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.39,0:16:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个叛徒 爱的代价我可是会算得很高的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.39,0:16:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚叶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.31,0:16:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jin君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jin君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.71,0:16:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.26,0:16:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会被区区思念体干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jin君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 赶快合体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:16:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好 Jin 我们合体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔 御子乃 联弹合体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,GO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硝烟合体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,GO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能与大家心意相通
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.11,0:17:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这正是两股相互交织的轰鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.85,0:17:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 力量不断涌现
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.55,0:17:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跨越两颗星球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.98,0:17:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion Gepard
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion Spada
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:53.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音色不错啊 挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.35,0:18:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游戏到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.47,0:18:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么声响
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去会承受不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚叶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.50,0:18:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Element 灵气等级低下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命体征出现紊乱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:41.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家有生命危险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jin君 刚才的伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么好介意的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不想再看到…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:18:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.34,0:19:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jin君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚叶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:15.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jin
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jin
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.99,0:19:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jin
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.74,0:19:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渐渐联系在了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那光晕是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超越星辰而联系在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无限大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:20:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 Gepard召唤出了新的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gepard在进化!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是Jin君的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人由Spada来牵制住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.57,0:20:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧 挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.97,0:20:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了将邪恶的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.60,0:20:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一刀两断
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:36.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里形成了阻断次元门的屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.56,0:20:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做个了结吧 阿马塔 御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一同奏响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旋律的冬之喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逆转吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.07,0:21:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.89,0:21:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,致命一击的叠句
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次元门已被遮断 Gepard Spada双双健在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.90,0:22:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们赢了 Jin君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jin君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.63,0:22:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚叶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.90,0:22:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能与你相遇的奇迹 让我快要停止呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.20,0:22:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧牵你的手 让我觉得自己能稍微变强一点
